#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/earth-day.tsx:181
msgid "Most environmental gains start small and local: a restored wetland, a cleaner stretch of river, a species given just enough room to recover."
msgstr "大多数环境改善从小处、从本地做起：一片恢复的湿地、一段更清洁的河流、一个获得足够空间得以恢复的物种。"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/leonids.tsx:89
msgid "Most years the display is modest, but the shower is famous for its capacity to produce rare and spectacular surprises."
msgstr "多数年份的景象较为克制，但它以罕见而壮观的惊喜能力闻名。"

